msgctxt " 	　	　	117	6357	6240"
msgid "All fake. I mean, I <Italic>did</Italic> stab him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	177	6576	6399"
msgid "I had to make you lash out at Kugihara\\r\n"
"somehow, and that was my only option."
