msgctxt " 	　	分	86	6934	6848"
msgid "A waste of effort, but it needed to be done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	181	7160	6979"
msgid "So, we pulled the necessary strings.\\r\n"
"Made you <Italic>want</Italic> to break out."
